(140, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/05/wordpress-4-2-2/''>WordPress 4.2.2 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">May 7, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.2.2 is now available. This is a critical security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. Version 4.2.2 addresses two security issues: The Genericons icon font package, which is used in a number of popular themes and plugins, contained an HTML file vulnerable to a cross-site [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-core-contributors-call-for-user-testing-on-the-menu-customizer-plugin''>WPTavern: WordPress Core Contributors Call for User Testing on the Menu Customizer Plugin</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/06/trust-but-preview/''>Matt: Trust but Preview</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/introducing-the-wp-tavern-wapuu''>WPTavern: Introducing the WP Tavern Wapuu</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/responsive-lightbox/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Responsive Lightbox by dFactory</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=responsive-lightbox&amp;_wpnonce=fd9125ab71&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Responsive Lightbox by dFactory''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
