(17, 1, '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '<strong>Direct Tax Consultancy Services</strong>\r\n\r\nTaxation being a highly specialized area requires skills relating to tax planning, documentation and representations. We provide under-mentioned services to our clients:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>¬†<strong>Preparation of tax returns for Individuals, Firms, NRI''s, Foreign Nationals, Companies etc.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>¬†<strong>Representing clients and appearing before various authorities which includes;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>a) Assessing Officer</li>\r\n	<li>b) Appellate Authorities</li>\r\n	<li>c) Tribunal</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li></li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† *¬†<strong>Tax Planning Services - Personal and Corporate.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬†* ¬†<strong>Tax Assistance</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>a) Obtaining Permanent Account Number</li>\r\n	<li>b) Tax Deduction Account Number</li>\r\n	<li>c) Services related to TDS/ Withholding taxes</li>\r\n	<li>d) Tax Planning - Personal and Corporate.</li>\r\n	<li>e) Filing of e-Income tax and e-TDS returns</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nf)¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† STPI registration\r\n\r\n<strong>International tax planning services - International Taxation</strong>\r\n\r\nInbound &amp; outbound investments together with obtaining the necessary approvals &amp; permits from the regulatory authorities viz Reserve Bank of India (RBI), Foreign Exchange Promotion Board (FIPB) &amp; Secretariat of Industrial Assurances (SIA) together with Liaison with Directorate General of Foreign Trade (DGFT) and Ministry of Industries.\r\n\r\n<strong>Transfer Pricing</strong>¬†:- Assisting Companies in the Transfer Pricing rules in India together with certification &amp; filing of necessary reports.\r\n\r\nNRI &amp; Overseas Consultation to develop strategies for tax minimization together with setting up of Offshore Companies keeping in view the Double Taxation Avoidance Agreement (DTAA) rules &amp; regulations of the Foreign jurisdiction.\r\n\r\n<strong>Service Tax</strong>\r\n\r\nRepresentation and Assistance Services\r\n\r\nRepresentation for Assessment and other proceedings in the tax department\r\n\r\nRepresentation in Appeals before Commissioner (Appeals)\r\n\r\nRepresentation in Appeals before Income Tax Appellate Tribunal (ITAT)\r\n\r\nRepresentation before Income Tax Settlement Commission\r\n\r\nRepresentation before Authority for Advance Rulings (AAR)', 'Taxation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'taxation', '', '', '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/?page_id=17', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(18, 1, '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '<strong>Direct Tax Consultancy Services</strong>\r\n\r\nTaxation being a highly specialized area requires skills relating to tax planning, documentation and representations. We provide under-mentioned services to our clients:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>¬†<strong>Preparation of tax returns for Individuals, Firms, NRI''s, Foreign Nationals, Companies etc.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>¬†<strong>Representing clients and appearing before various authorities which includes;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>a) Assessing Officer</li>\r\n	<li>b) Appellate Authorities</li>\r\n	<li>c) Tribunal</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li></li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† *¬†<strong>Tax Planning Services - Personal and Corporate.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬†* ¬†<strong>Tax Assistance</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>a) Obtaining Permanent Account Number</li>\r\n	<li>b) Tax Deduction Account Number</li>\r\n	<li>c) Services related to TDS/ Withholding taxes</li>\r\n	<li>d) Tax Planning - Personal and Corporate.</li>\r\n	<li>e) Filing of e-Income tax and e-TDS returns</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nf)¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† STPI registration\r\n\r\n<strong>International tax planning services - International Taxation</strong>\r\n\r\nInbound &amp; outbound investments together with obtaining the necessary approvals &amp; permits from the regulatory authorities viz Reserve Bank of India (RBI), Foreign Exchange Promotion Board (FIPB) &amp; Secretariat of Industrial Assurances (SIA) together with Liaison with Directorate General of Foreign Trade (DGFT) and Ministry of Industries.\r\n\r\n<strong>Transfer Pricing</strong>¬†:- Assisting Companies in the Transfer Pricing rules in India together with certification &amp; filing of necessary reports.\r\n\r\nNRI &amp; Overseas Consultation to develop strategies for tax minimization together with setting up of Offshore Companies keeping in view the Double Taxation Avoidance Agreement (DTAA) rules &amp; regulations of the Foreign jurisdiction.\r\n\r\n<strong>Service Tax</strong>\r\n\r\nRepresentation and Assistance Services\r\n\r\nRepresentation for Assessment and other proceedings in the tax department\r\n\r\nRepresentation in Appeals before Commissioner (Appeals)\r\n\r\nRepresentation in Appeals before Income Tax Appellate Tribunal (ITAT)\r\n\r\nRepresentation before Income Tax Settlement Commission\r\n\r\nRepresentation before Authority for Advance Rulings (AAR)', 'Taxation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '2015-06-11 09:57:40', '', 17, 'http://localhost/adityaser/2015/06/11/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(19, 1, '2015-06-11 09:58:47', '2015-06-11 09:58:47', 'You can digitally sign a document for many of the same reasons why you might place a handwritten signature on a paper document. A digital signature is used to help authenticate the identity of the creator of digital information¬†‚Äî such as documents, e-mail messages, and macros¬†‚Äî by using cryptographic algorithms.\r\n\r\nDigital signatures are based on digital certificates. Digital certificates are verifiers of identity issued by a trusted third party, which is known as a Certification Authority (CA). This works similarly to the use of standard identity documents in a non-electronic environment. For example, a trusted third party such as a government entity or employer issues identity documents¬†‚Äî such as driver‚Äôs licenses, passports and employee ID cards¬†‚Äî on which others rely to verify that a person is whom he or she claims to be.\r\n\r\nDigital certificates can be issued by CAs within an organization, such as a Windows Server 2003 server that is running Windows Certificate Services, or a public CA, such as VeriSign or Thawed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhat digital signatures accomplish?\r\n\r\nDigital signatures help establish the following authentication measures:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Authenticity</strong>¬†¬†¬†The digital signature helps ensure that the signer is whom he or she claims to be. This helps prevent others from pretending to be the originator of a particular document (the¬†equivalent of forgery on a printed document). <strong>Integrity</strong>¬†¬†¬†The digital signature helps ensure that the content has not been changed or tampered with since it was digitally signed. This helps prevent documents from being intercepted and changed without knowledge of the originator of the document.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Digital Signature Certificate', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'digital-signature-certificate', '', '', '2015-06-11 09:58:47', '2015-06-11 09:58:47', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/?page_id=19', 1, 'page', '', 0),
(20, 1, '2015-06-11 09:58:47', '2015-06-11 09:58:47', 'You can digitally sign a document for many of the same reasons why you might place a handwritten signature on a paper document. A digital signature is used to help authenticate the identity of the creator of digital information¬†‚Äî such as documents, e-mail messages, and macros¬†‚Äî by using cryptographic algorithms.\r\n\r\nDigital signatures are based on digital certificates. Digital certificates are verifiers of identity issued by a trusted third party, which is known as a Certification Authority (CA). This works similarly to the use of standard identity documents in a non-electronic environment. For example, a trusted third party such as a government entity or employer issues identity documents¬†‚Äî such as driver‚Äôs licenses, passports and employee ID cards¬†‚Äî on which others rely to verify that a person is whom he or she claims to be.\r\n\r\nDigital certificates can be issued by CAs within an organization, such as a Windows Server 2003 server that is running Windows Certificate Services, or a public CA, such as VeriSign or Thawed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhat digital signatures accomplish?\r\n\r\nDigital signatures help establish the following authentication measures:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Authenticity</strong>¬†¬†¬†The digital signature helps ensure that the signer is whom he or she claims to be. This helps prevent others from pretending to be the originator of a particular document (the¬†equivalent of forgery on a printed document). <strong>Integrity</strong>¬†¬†¬†The digital signature helps ensure that the content has not been changed or tampered with since it was digitally signed. This helps prevent documents from being intercepted and changed without knowledge of the originator of the document.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Digital Signature Certificate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-11 09:58:47', '2015-06-11 09:58:47', '', 19, 'http://localhost/adityaser/2015/06/11/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(21, 1, '2015-06-11 10:04:26', '2015-06-11 10:04:26', 'Our Accounting Advisory Services is a dedicated team of professionals with in-depth technical accounting knowledge, capital markets insight and substantial industry experience. Our teams are experienced in advising clients on challenging, complex issues arising from transactions, business decisions and regulatory changes.\r\n\r\nGeneral ledger and financial statement preparation Accounting system setup for new businesses Computerized payroll services Bookkeeping Design, implementation and review of accounting manual Personal financial statements Advice on various accounting issues\r\n\r\nIt is essential that all businesses set themselves targets and encompass them into a business plan. We can assist you in setting the targets and then prepare budgets and cash flow forecasts so you can measure your business progress against those targets. Part of the budget process will allow you to utilise tools and techniques which will enable you to consider future scenarios and give you goals to strive for in your business. Banks and financiers are insisting on detailed projections as part of the process of acquiring funding. Cash flow forecasting is a vital part of ensuring that your business will always have the cash it needs, because profits don‚Äôt pay bills - cash does.\r\n\r\nWe are offering to our valued customers a supreme quality range of Agreements and Deeds. We give our best opinion to our clients and try to give mutual agreement which is beneficial to both the parties. Together with these services we are also providing services for Firm registration, Partnership Deed, Modification and Changes in Partnership firm, Proprietorship Registration, PF Registration, Rent Agreements, Lease Agreements, NOC, and Contract Agreements.', 'ACCOUNTING ADVISORY SERVICES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'accounting-advisory-services', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:04:26', '2015-06-11 10:04:26', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/?page_id=21', 2, 'page', '', 0),
