siness valuations</li>\r\n	<li>Buying/selling a business</li>\r\n	<li>Computer systems</li>\r\n	<li>Financial &amp; retirement decisions</li>\r\n	<li>Estate, trust &amp; gift planning</li>\r\n</ul>', 'CONSULTANCY SERVICES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'consultancy-services', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:05:18', '2015-06-11 10:05:18', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/?page_id=23', 3, 'page', '', 0),
