(25, 1, '2015-06-11 10:07:06', '2015-06-11 10:07:06', 'All Private and Public limited companies are governed by the Companies Act, 1956 in India. Limited Companies have limited liabilities and are to be run in accordance with the Companies Act &amp; Rules.\r\n\r\nOur services under the Company Law matters comprises of:\r\n\r\n<strong>Company Formation:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe process of formation of new companies has been eased substantially by Registrar of Companies and today new companies can be formed much easily and quickly. From name availability for new company, getting DIN for new directors, from drafting of memorandum and articles of new companies till the final process of Company registration, we do everything. So be rest assured that your new company registration will be done easily and quickly.\r\n\r\n<strong>Company Secretarial matters:</strong>\r\n\r\nOnce the company is formed we can take care of all secretarial compliances related to company law matters for the newly formed company or for any existing Private or Public Limited Companies.\r\n\r\n<strong>Company ROC Filing and Compliances:</strong>\r\n\r\nLike Income Tax Return Filing which is to be done annually, after the formation of Companies annual filing is to be done of companies too, with the Registrar of Companies or the ROC. The common forms used for annual filing of ROC is 23AC, 23 ACA, 20B, Form 66 etc.\r\n\r\nOther Company Law Services which we are providing are as under:\r\n\r\nCompany Accounting matters\r\n\r\nCompany Capital and dividend distribution\r\n\r\nCompany Internal and Statutory audit\r\n\r\nCompany Winding-Up', 'COMPANY LAW MATTERS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'company-law-matters', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:07:06', '2015-06-11 10:07:06', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/?page_id=25', 4, 'page', '', 0),
(26, 1, '2015-06-11 10:07:06', '2015-06-11 10:07:06', 'All Private and Public limited companies are governed by the Companies Act, 1956 in India. Limited Companies have limited liabilities and are to be run in accordance with the Companies Act &amp; Rules.\r\n\r\nOur services under the Company Law matters comprises of:\r\n\r\n<strong>Company Formation:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe process of formation of new companies has been eased substantially by Registrar of Companies and today new companies can be formed much easily and quickly. From name availability for new company, getting DIN for new directors, from drafting of memorandum and articles of new companies till the final process of Company registration, we do everything. So be rest assured that your new company registration will be done easily and quickly.\r\n\r\n<strong>Company Secretarial matters:</strong>\r\n\r\nOnce the company is formed we can take care of all secretarial compliances related to company law matters for the newly formed company or for any existing Private or Public Limited Companies.\r\n\r\n<strong>Company ROC Filing and Compliances:</strong>\r\n\r\nLike Income Tax Return Filing which is to be done annually, after the formation of Companies annual filing is to be done of companies too, with the Registrar of Companies or the ROC. The common forms used for annual filing of ROC is 23AC, 23 ACA, 20B, Form 66 etc.\r\n\r\nOther Company Law Services which we are providing are as under:\r\n\r\nCompany Accounting matters\r\n\r\nCompany Capital and dividend distribution\r\n\r\nCompany Internal and Statutory audit\r\n\r\nCompany Winding-Up', 'COMPANY LAW MATTERS', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:07:06', '2015-06-11 10:07:06', '', 25, 'http://localhost/adityaser/2015/06/11/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
