(27, 1, '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '<strong>Assurance Services</strong>\r\n\r\nOur commitment to delivering high-quality assurance services is at the heart of what we do. We provide comprehensive audit and assurance services designed to deliver real value and underpin investor confidence.¬† We invite you to explore the many ways our professionals can help you. Our commitment to delivering high-quality assurance services is at the heart of what we do. We provide comprehensive audit and assurance services designed to deliver real value and underpin investor confidence.¬† We invite you to explore the many ways our professionals can help you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Audit and Other Assignments</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬†<strong>. ¬†</strong>¬† ¬†¬†Tax Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Company Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† VAT Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Statutory audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Internal audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† System audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Management Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Concurrent and Income &amp; Expenditure audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Bank audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Operations and Efficiency Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Financial impropriety and fraud audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Due diligence\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Special Investigative Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Stock audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Certification work\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Review Of TDS Compliance\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Transfer Pricing Audit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Certification of Financial Data / Statements</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can count on us for putting together a concise, organized statement that you may immediately present to your financial institution, private banker, or merely to keep onsite as a great guide for future years.\r\n\r\n<strong>Charitable Trusts Matters</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†¬† Registration of Charitable Trust</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Registration of Charitable Trust under Societies Registration Act or ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† Companies Act</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Registration under Income-tax Act u/s. 12AA of I.T. Act</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Exemption Certificate U/s. 80G of Income Tax Act</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Filing Objection Memo/other Replies</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Filing of Annual Budget</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAttending before Charity Commissioner including for Attending Objections\r\n\r\n-¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Formation &amp; Registration of company\r\n\r\n-¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† E- Filing of Documents with MCA.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>- Compliance under Companies Act, 1956</li>\r\n	<li>- Getting the Company name changed</li>\r\n	<li>- Formation of Section 25 Company</li>\r\n	<li>- Getting Charge Registered</li>\r\n	<li>- Liaison with Registrar of Companies &amp; Regional Directors</li>\r\n	<li>- Getting Director Identification Number (DIN)</li>\r\n	<li>- Maintenance of statutory records prescribed under Companies Act, 1956</li>\r\n	<li>- All matters related with Registrar of Companies &amp; Company Law Board</li>\r\n	<li>- Maintenance &amp; compliance of Statutory Records</li>\r\n	<li>- Consultancy in above matters</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Custom Duty Matters</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are providing wide assortment of Customs Clearance. We have been able to establish ourselves as a prominent leader in the industry. We are recognized for our specialization, efficiency and commitment to quality. These services are available at market competitive prices.\r\n\r\n<strong>Excise Duty Matters</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are also engaged in offering Central Excise services to our customers. We are offering all services for Central Excise i.e. Excise Registration, Excise Returns, Excise Record Maintaining, Excise Valuation, Excise Credits, Excise Appeal.\r\n\r\n<strong>FEMA Matters</strong>\r\n\r\nIndia Entry Strategies for\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>- Liaison Offices</li>\r\n	<li>- Branch Offices</li>\r\n	<li>- Project Offices</li>\r\n	<li>- Subsidiaries</li>\r\n	<li>- Joint Ventures etc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Finance Management Services</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For Corporate Clients/ Non Corporate Clients.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of fund flow and cash flow statements and forecasts.</li>\r\n	<li>Projection of working capital requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of project reports.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and processing of loan applications.</li>\r\n	<li>Amalgamation and merger schemes.</li>\r\n	<li>Planning capital structure.</li>\r\n	<li>Drafting of Memorandum and Articles of Association.</li>\r\n	<li>Formation of companies.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and Analysis of Prospectus.</li>\r\n	<li>Raising of Capital, new issues and matters concerned therewith including SEBI Guidelines.</li>\r\n	<li>Drafting of Minutes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insolvency/Liquidation Proceedings.</li>\r\n	<li>Work study.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizational Structure Consultancy.</li>\r\n	<li>Design and conduct of training ¬†¬†programmers.</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Planning.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Financial Research Services</strong>\r\n\r\nThrough thought-provoking publications, surveys and reports as well as insightful commentary, We deliver innovative, practical knowledge companies can use to improve their overall business performance. Our professionals and senior consultants can identify, analyze and help explain the issues critical to businesses across a variety of industries.\r\n\r\nIn our Financial Services research area, you will find thought leadership and commentary on topics including offshoring, cost reduction, customer retention, and mergers and acquisitions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Inbound and Outbound Investment related Services</strong>\r\n\r\nWe understand the importance of sound Inbound / Outbound Investment strategy as it is essential to achieve the business objectives of cross-border investments. Although substantially liberalized, there can be various situations under which approvals may be required to invest in India / outside India. Businesses may also require approvals for cross-border loans.\r\n\r\nWe offer following services for inbound / outbound investment -\r\n\r\n- Formulating an entry strategy into India, like - establishing a Liaison Office, a branch office, a subsidiary, etc.\r\n\r\n- Formulating an appropriate foreign investment consultancy services for companies seeking to invest out of India\r\n\r\n- Obtaining investment approvals from the Foreign Investment Promotion Board (FIPB) or the Reserve Bank of India, as required\r\n\r\n- Assistance in obtaining approvals for External Commercial Borrowings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Insurance and Risk Management Services</strong>\r\n\r\nRisk &amp; Compliance Services includes multidisciplinary team of professionals experienced in financial and operational fraud analytics and risk assessment. We aim to make efficient and effective internal audit functions, Enterprise Risk Management programs, and risk and controls management.\r\n\r\nOur range of services that helps the business leaders for their complex matters, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Enterprise Risk Management</li>\r\n	<li>Regulatory compliance</li>\r\n	<li>Contract compliance</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate governance</li>\r\n	<li>Continuous auditing / monitoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe offer a broad range of financial risk management service:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Credit risk measurement and management.</li>\r\n	<li>Operational risk measurement and management.</li>\r\n	<li>Capital adequacy &amp; regulatory services.</li>\r\n	<li>Actuarial services &amp; financial statement support.</li>\r\n	<li>Financial instruments accounting.</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance risk assessment.</li>\r\n	<li>Basel III and Solvency III transformation.</li>\r\n	<li>Quantitative evaluation and management of portfolio risks.</li>\r\n	<li>Financial engineering.</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management in transactions.</li>\r\n	<li>Asset management advisory.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>LLP Matters</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Name Reservation Service</li>\r\n	<li>Annual Filing Services</li>\r\n	<li>Induction of New Partners and changes thereof</li>\r\n	<li>Conversion of Firms / Companies to LLP</li>\r\n	<li>Conversion of LLP to Company (under Part IX of the¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Companies Act,1956</li>\r\n	<li>Compromise, Arrangement or Reconstruction of Limited Liability Partnerships</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Merger and Acquisition Transaction Services</strong>\r\n\r\nMergers &amp; Acquisitions (M&amp;A) Tax practice helps businesses with cross-state border M&amp;A and other transactions. We offer wide range of M&amp;A tax services to corporate and private equity investors covering all phases of domestic and nation-wide transactions.\r\n\r\nOur services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tax due diligence</li>\r\n	<li>Structuring an acquisition or disposition</li>\r\n	<li>Tax modelling</li>\r\n	<li>Vendor assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Post-deal integration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Outsourcing of Services</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>International Accounting, Finance and Taxation</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and filing of Tax Return</li>\r\n	<li>Payroll Administration &amp; Customized Payroll Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of management accounts and management information systems</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation &amp; Maintenance of books of accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Support in day to day Transaction Processing</li>\r\n	<li>Book keeping and preparation of final accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Fixed Assets verification and completion of records</li>\r\n	<li>Data processing and also architecture related services</li>\r\n</ul>', 'PROFESSIONAL WORKS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'professional-works', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/?page_id=27', 5, 'page', '', 0),
(28, 1, '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '<strong>Assurance Services</strong>\r\n\r\nOur commitment to delivering high-quality assurance services is at the heart of what we do. We provide comprehensive audit and assurance services designed to deliver real value and underpin investor confidence.¬† We invite you to explore the many ways our professionals can help you. Our commitment to delivering high-quality assurance services is at the heart of what we do. We provide comprehensive audit and assurance services designed to deliver real value and underpin investor confidence.¬† We invite you to explore the many ways our professionals can help you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Audit and Other Assignments</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬†<strong>. ¬†</strong>¬† ¬†¬†Tax Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Company Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† VAT Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Statutory audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Internal audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† System audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Management Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Concurrent and Income &amp; Expenditure audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Bank audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Operations and Efficiency Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Financial impropriety and fraud audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Due diligence\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Special Investigative Audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Stock audit\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Certification work\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Review Of TDS Compliance\r\n¬∑¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Transfer Pricing Audit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Certification of Financial Data / Statements</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can count on us for putting together a concise, organized statement that you may immediately present to your financial institution, private banker, or merely to keep onsite as a great guide for future years.\r\n\r\n<strong>Charitable Trusts Matters</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†¬† Registration of Charitable Trust</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Registration of Charitable Trust under Societies Registration Act or ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† Companies Act</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Registration under Income-tax Act u/s. 12AA of I.T. Act</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Exemption Certificate U/s. 80G of Income Tax Act</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Filing Objection Memo/other Replies</li>\r\n	<li>¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬†Filing of Annual Budget</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAttending before Charity Commissioner including for Attending Objections\r\n\r\n-¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Formation &amp; Registration of company\r\n\r\n-¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† E- Filing of Documents with MCA.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>- Compliance under Companies Act, 1956</li>\r\n	<li>- Getting the Company name changed</li>\r\n	<li>- Formation of Section 25 Company</li>\r\n	<li>- Getting Charge Registered</li>\r\n	<li>- Liaison with Registrar of Companies &amp; Regional Directors</li>\r\n	<li>- Getting Director Identification Number (DIN)</li>\r\n	<li>- Maintenance of statutory records prescribed under Companies Act, 1956</li>\r\n	<li>- All matters related with Registrar of Companies &amp; Company Law Board</li>\r\n	<li>- Maintenance &amp; compliance of Statutory Records</li>\r\n	<li>- Consultancy in above matters</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Custom Duty Matters</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are providing wide assortment of Customs Clearance. We have been able to establish ourselves as a prominent leader in the industry. We are recognized for our specialization, efficiency and commitment to quality. These services are available at market competitive prices.\r\n\r\n<strong>Excise Duty Matters</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are also engaged in offering Central Excise services to our customers. We are offering all services for Central Excise i.e. Excise Registration, Excise Returns, Excise Record Maintaining, Excise Valuation, Excise Credits, Excise Appeal.\r\n\r\n<strong>FEMA Matters</strong>\r\n\r\nIndia Entry Strategies for\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>- Liaison Offices</li>\r\n	<li>- Branch Offices</li>\r\n	<li>- Project Offices</li>\r\n	<li>- Subsidiaries</li>\r\n	<li>- Joint Ventures etc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Finance Management Services</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For Corporate Clients/ Non Corporate Clients.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of fund flow and cash flow statements and forecasts.</li>\r\n	<li>Projection of working capital requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of project reports.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and processing of loan applications.</li>\r\n	<li>Amalgamation and merger schemes.</li>\r\n	<li>Planning capital structure.</li>\r\n	<li>Drafting of Memorandum and Articles of Association.</li>\r\n	<li>Formation of companies.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and Analysis of Prospectus.</li>\r\n	<li>Raising of Capital, new issues and matters concerned therewith including SEBI Guidelines.</li>\r\n	<li>Drafting of Minutes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insolvency/Liquidation Proceedings.</li>\r\n	<li>Work study.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizational Structure Consultancy.</li>\r\n	<li>Design and conduct of training ¬†¬†programmers.</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Planning.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Financial Research Services</strong>\r\n\r\nThrough thought-provoking publications, surveys and reports as well as insightful commentary, We deliver innovative, practical knowledge companies can use to improve their overall business performance. Our professionals and senior consultants can identify, analyze and help explain the issues critical to businesses across a variety of industries.\r\n\r\nIn our Financial Services research area, you will find thought leadership and commentary on topics including offshoring, cost reduction, customer retention, and mergers and acquisitions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Inbound and Outbound Investment related Services</strong>\r\n\r\nWe understand the importance of sound Inbound / Outbound Investment strategy as it is essential to achieve the business objectives of cross-border investments. Although substantially liberalized, there can be various situations under which approvals may be required to invest in India / outside India. Businesses may also require approvals for cross-border loans.\r\n\r\nWe offer following services for inbound / outbound investment -\r\n\r\n- Formulating an entry strategy into India, like - establishing a Liaison Office, a branch office, a subsidiary, etc.\r\n\r\n- Formulating an appropriate foreign investment consultancy services for companies seeking to invest out of India\r\n\r\n- Obtaining investment approvals from the Foreign Investment Promotion Board (FIPB) or the Reserve Bank of India, as required\r\n\r\n- Assistance in obtaining approvals for External Commercial Borrowings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Insurance and Risk Management Services</strong>\r\n\r\nRisk &amp; Compliance Services includes multidisciplinary team of professionals experienced in financial and operational fraud analytics and risk assessment. We aim to make efficient and effective internal audit functions, Enterprise Risk Management programs, and risk and controls management.\r\n\r\nOur range of services that helps the business leaders for their complex matters, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Enterprise Risk Management</li>\r\n	<li>Regulatory compliance</li>\r\n	<li>Contract compliance</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate governance</li>\r\n	<li>Continuous auditing / monitoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe offer a broad range of financial risk management service:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Credit risk measurement and management.</li>\r\n	<li>Operational risk measurement and management.</li>\r\n	<li>Capital adequacy &amp; regulatory services.</li>\r\n	<li>Actuarial services &amp; financial statement support.</li>\r\n	<li>Financial instruments accounting.</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance risk assessment.</li>\r\n	<li>Basel III and Solvency III transformation.</li>\r\n	<li>Quantitative evaluation and management of portfolio risks.</li>\r\n	<li>Financial engineering.</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management in transactions.</li>\r\n	<li>Asset management advisory.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>LLP Matters</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Name Reservation Service</li>\r\n	<li>Annual Filing Services</li>\r\n	<li>Induction of New Partners and changes thereof</li>\r\n	<li>Conversion of Firms / Companies to LLP</li>\r\n	<li>Conversion of LLP to Company (under Part IX of the¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬† Companies Act,1956</li>\r\n	<li>Compromise, Arrangement or Reconstruction of Limited Liability Partnerships</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Merger and Acquisition Transaction Services</strong>\r\n\r\nMergers &amp; Acquisitions (M&amp;A) Tax practice helps businesses with cross-state border M&amp;A and other transactions. We offer wide range of M&amp;A tax services to corporate and private equity investors covering all phases of domestic and nation-wide transactions.\r\n\r\nOur services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tax due diligence</li>\r\n	<li>Structuring an acquisition or disposition</li>\r\n	<li>Tax modelling</li>\r\n	<li>Vendor assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Post-deal integration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Outsourcing of Services</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>International Accounting, Finance and Taxation</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and filing of Tax Return</li>\r\n	<li>Payroll Administration &amp; Customized Payroll Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of management accounts and management information systems</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation &amp; Maintenance of books of accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Support in day to day Transaction Processing</li>\r\n	<li>Book keeping and preparation of final accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Fixed Assets verification and completion of records</li>\r\n	<li>Data processing and also architecture related services</li>\r\n</ul>', 'PROFESSIONAL WORKS', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '2015-06-11 10:08:30', '', 27, 'http://localhost/adityaser/2015/06/11/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
