(30, 1, '2015-06-11 10:13:20', '2015-06-11 10:13:20', '<div class="container1">\r\n<div class="service-description column-one-half">\r\n<h4>TAXATION</h4>\r\n<p align="justify">Direct Tax Consultancy Services Taxation being a highly specialized area requires skills relating to tax planning, documentation and representations. We provide under-mentioned services to our clients: ¬∑¬† ¬†Preparation of tax returns for Individuals, Firms, NRI'' . . .<a class="link1" href="http://localhost/adityaser/services/taxation/">more</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="service-description column-one-half">\r\n<h4>DIGITAL SIGNATURE CERTIFICATE</h4>\r\n<p align="justify">You can digitally sign a document for many of the same reasons why you might place a handwritten signature on a paper document. A digital signature is used to help authenticate the identity of the creator of digital information¬†‚Äî such as documents, e-mail messages, and . . .<a class="link1" href="http://bpspl.com/index.php?strServiceID=49#Expert_SendMessage">more</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="service-description column-one-half">\r\n<h4>ACCOUNTING ADVISORY SERVICES</h4>\r\n<p align="justify">Our Accounting Advisory Services is a dedicated team of professionals with in-depth technical accounting knowledge, capital markets insight and substantial industry experience. Our teams are experienced in advising clients on challenging, complex issues arising from transactions, . . .<a class="link1" href="http://localhost/adityaser/services/accounting-advisory-services/">more</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="service-description column-one-half">\r\n<h4>CONSULTANCY SERVICES</h4>\r\n<p align="justify">We are engaged in offering quality assurance Management Consulting services. Owing to our professional business approach and innovative strategies, we are able to exhibit reliability and high performance in this market leading price .We provides the services of Loan and Project F . . .<a class="link1" href="http://localhost/adityaser/services/consultancy-services/">more</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="service-description column-one-half">\r\n<h4>COMPANY LAW MATTERS</h4>\r\n<p align="justify">All Private and Public limited companies are governed by the Companies Act, 1956 in India. Limited Companies have limited liabilities and are to be run in accordance with the Companies Act &amp; Rules. Our services under the Company Law matters comprises of: Company Formation: . . .<a class="link1" href="http://localhost/adityaser/services/company-law-matters/">more</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="service-description column-one-half">\r\n<h4>PROFESSIONAL WORKS</h4>\r\n<p align="justify">Assurance Services Our commitment to delivering high-quality assurance services is at the heart of what we do. We provide comprehensive audit and assurance services designed to deliver real value and underpin investor confidence.¬† We invite you to explore the many ways our . . .<a class="link1" href="http://localhost/adityaser/services/professional-works/">more</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-11 10:13:20', '2015-06-11 10:13:20', '', 13, 'http://localhost/adityaser/2015/06/11/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
